<! [CDATA[
 Yandex (Яндекс) Logo
Yandex N.V. is a Russian Dutch-domiciled multinational corporation providing over 70 Internet-related products and services, including transportation, search and information services, eCommerce, navigation, mobile applications, and online advertising. The firm is registered in Schiphol, the Netherlands as a naamloze vennootschap, but the company founders and most of the team members are located in Russia. It primarily serves audiences in Russia and the Commonwealth of Independent States, and also has 18 commercial offices worldwide.
